briefdescription.para: Murmur3_86_128 (folded to 64 bits).
Open-addressed hashmap (Robin Hood), with allocator udata support.

detaileddescription.para: Updated by Craig Edwards, September 2025, to allow udata to be passed to the allocator functions. This enables contextual/arena allocators (e.g., per BASIC interpreter context) without altering external call sites.
